snippet.title: Galaxy of Pen & Paper - Teaser
snippet.description:
www.galaxyofpenandpaper.com.br - Behold Studios

Teaser trailer for the upcoming sequel to the Pen & Paper franchise. Galaxy of Pen & Paper sets this new adventure in space, creating a whole new game from the ground up, including the classic turn based battle, old school art and outstanding humor!
